Hey everyone! I just launched the MVP for Essen, a marketplace for men’s personal care products. DM our instagram account @essen.menscare with your specific skincare or grooming questions, and our team will recommend products to you. If you are interested in trying them, we’ll fulfill it for you too. Thanks and let me know if you have feedback or questions!

Some sample questions:

- My skin is oily, what moisturizer should I use? - How can I prevent dandruff? - What’s a basic skincare routine to improve the condition of my skin? - How do I delay wrinkles?
